 2. PROHIBITION OF INVERSE DERIVATION (CAUSAL DIODE)
===========================================================================
Any logic, algorithm, or modification that derives internal force, 
potential, or state from external results—including but not limited to 
Distance, Geometric Radii (e.g., center-to-edge), or Resultant 
Coordinates—is STRICTLY PROHIBITED. 
Distance must remain a "Projection (Log)" and shall not be used as an 
input or intermediate driver for causal dynamics.

